name: Stephen Colbert
description:
follow me on Instagram, Youtube, Patreon and my website.

Stephen Colbert

Suggested Weight: 0.6-1.0

Suggested prompts

  • photo of c0183rt as a wizard wearing a wizard hat and holding a magic wand, light bokeh, intricate detail

  • Don't be scared to turn the weight all the way down (even lower than 0.6)

  • You will need to inpaint the face often

  • prone to noise/overexposure if you try adding too much detail in prompts

Training

  • trained on ~24 images

  • Learning Rate: 0.005:1000, 0.001:2000, 0.0001:5000, 0.00005

  • Total Steps: 15,000

  • Batch Size: 1

  • Gradient Steps: 1
